Module kivakit.core
Package com.telenav.kivakit.core.time

Class HourOfWeekSpan

java.lang.Object
com.telenav.kivakit.core.time.HourOfWeekSpan
public class HourOfWeekSpan extends Object
Represents a span of hours of the week in a local timezone. For example, monday at 3pm to tuesday at 1pm in the Pacific timezone (PT).
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
